quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  30,33,"N’iyo abantu bagezweho n’ingorane, basaba Nyagasani wabo bamwicuzaho. Maze yabasogongeza ku mpuhwe ze (abakiza izo ngorane), bamwe muri bo (bakongera) bakabangikanya (Nyagasani wabo),",""
  30,34,"Kugira ngo bahakane ibyo twabahaye (tubarokora). Ngaho nimwinezeze ariko (bidatinze) muzaba mumenya (ingaruka z’ibyo mwakoze).",""
  30,35,"Ahubwo se twaba twarabamanuriye ikimenyetso simusiga (igitabo), kikaba ari cyo kivuga (ukuri kw’) ibyo bamubangikanya na byo?",""
  30,36,"N’iyo dusogongeje abantu ku mpuhwe (ibyiza) barazishimira; ariko bagerwaho n’ingorane kubera ibyo bakoze, bakiheba.",""
  30,37,"Ese ntibabona ko Allah yongerera amafunguro uwo ashaka akanayagabanyiriza (uwo ashaka)? Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo inyigisho ku bantu bemera.",""
  30,38,"Bityo, umuvandimwe wawe wa hafi, umukene ndetse n’uri ku rugendo, ujye ubaha ibyo ubagomba. Ibyo ni byo byiza kuri ba bandi bashaka kwishimirwa na Allah, kandi abo ni bo bakiranutsi.",""
  30,39,"N’ibyo mutanga nka Riba<sup>1</sup> kugira ngo bitubukire mu mitungo y’abandi ntibishobora gutubuka kwa Allah. Ariko ibyo mutanga mu maturo mugamije kwishimirwa na Allah, abo (abakora nk’ibyo) ni bo bazatuburirwa (imitungo).","[1] Reba uko twasobanuye iri jambo muri Surat Al Baqarat, Ayat ya 275."
  30,40,"Allah ni We wabaremye maze abaha amafunguro, hanyuma akazabambura ubuzima (igihe cyo gupfa), akazanabubasubiza (igihe cy’izuka). Ese mu bigirwamana byanyu hari icyakora nk’ibyo? Ubutagatifu ni ubwe, kandi (Allah) nta ho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya na byo.",""
  30,41,"Ubwangizi bwagaragaye imusozi no mu nyanja kubera ibyo abantu bakoze bibi, kugira ngo (Allah) abasogongeze (ibihano) bya bimwe mu byo bakoze; bityo babashe kwisubiraho.",""
